#=======================================================================
#
# FILE:        Make.mach.nics-kraken-gnu
#
# DESCRIPTION: Makefile settings for NICS' Kraken using GNU
#
# AUTHOR:      Alexei Kritsuk
#
# DATE:        2008-05-31
# MODIFIED1:   John Wise (April 2010)
# MODIFIED1:   Matthew Turk (January 2011)
